>为一些病人、<span class="_ _6"></span>低贱的人</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y33 ffa fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">服务。 </div><div class="t m0 x22 h4 y26 ffa fs3 fc0 sc0 ls1f ws0">相比之下，如今<span class="_ _14"> </span>21<span class="_ _11"> </span>世纪，人类关于平等、关爱、和平</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y27 ffa fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">的理念，<span class="_ _8"></span>还没有达到佛陀所讲的万分之一。<span class="_ _8"></span>这一点不是我自</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y28 ffa fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">吹自擂，<span class="_ _19"></span>你们可以用自己的智慧、<span class="_ _19"></span>用探索的眼光，<span class="_ _19"></span>去翻开<span class="_ _19"></span>《毗</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 yd1 ffa fs3 fc0 sc0 ls42 ws0">奈耶经》<span class="_ _7"></span><span class="ls0">、<span class="_ _7"></span><span class="ls43">《长阿含经》<span class="_ _7"></span>，看看那时候的佛教思想成熟到什么</span></span></div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.500000,0.000000,0.000000,1.500000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
